<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><title>College Project: Etsy API Integration</title><style>body{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f8f8f8}.container{max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px;text-align:center;background-color:#fff;box-shadow:0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.1);border-radius:4px}h1{font-size:32px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#333}p{font-size:18px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#555}.btn{display:inline-block;padding:10px 20px;background-color:#007bff;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px;transition:background-color .3s ease}.btn:hover{background-color:#0056b3}</style></head><body><div class="container"><h1>College Project: Learning Buying and Purchasing with Etsy API</h1><p>Welcome to our college project landing page! We are a group of students who are passionate about exploring e-commerce platforms and APIs. Our project focuses on learning the buying and purchasing process using the Etsy API.</p><p>Through this project, we aim to gain hands-on experience with real-world APIs and understand the underlying mechanisms of e-commerce transactions. By integrating with the Etsy API, we can explore a vast marketplace of unique handmade and vintage items.</p><p>Feel free to join us on this exciting journey as we delve into the world of e-commerce and discover the possibilities of the Etsy platform.</p><a href="#" class="btn">Learn More</a></div></body></html>